data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the sought-after Cambria neighborhood! This 5-bed, 3-bath gem is a masterpiece with captivating features. Step inside to an inviting, open layout with a soothing neutral palette and abundant natural light. Tile flooring graces the main living areas, while carpeting adorns the bedrooms for comfort. The heart of this home is the fully equipped kitchen, a culinary enthusiast's dream. It boasts ample cabinet space, gleaming granite countertops, and essential appliances. The main suite is a private sanctuary with a lavish ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks, a separate shower and tub, and a spacious walk-in closet. In 2021, the house received fresh paint.  Other features:water softener, sun screens, extra attic insulation, duct sealing, smart thermostats and solar panels for energy efficiency. The master bath is a spa-like retreat. Don't miss this chance to make Cambria your forever home.
